# Using Commas in Print 


#### In the previous levels, you worked with **print statements** and strings.


<img src="https://images.code.org/3253ee1e2dd9ddd8b176930b996dd13f-image-1745270250476.png" alt="python code declaring variables and print statements" width="250px" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">

